Patch para adicionar serving estático da pasta uploads

No arquivo server/index.ts, adicionar após:
const clientPublicAssetsPath = path.join(process.cwd(), 'client', 'public', 'assets');

Adicionar:
const uploadsPath = path.join(process.cwd(), 'uploads');
if (fs.existsSync(uploadsPath)) {
  app.use('/uploads', express.static(uploadsPath));
  console.log('[Static] Serving uploads folder:', uploadsPath);
}
